INSTALLATION

- create a NEW local repo from the github repo on master branch
- copy crowdin/credentials.template to crowdin/credentials
- edit crowdin/credentials
  -> find the API-KEY here http://crowdin.net/project/rsandroidapp/settings#project-settings-api
- prepare crowdin:
  - run update manually

THE SCRIPTS

Run all scripts from within a repo.

- upload: no arguments
  -> this will upload the base language file values/strings.xml to crowdin.
    from master, it will upload to master and globals. other branches are not allowed.

- download: no arguments
  -> this will download the language files from crowdin.
